ue\" width=\"6\" height=\"4\" patternUnits=\"userSpaceOnUse\" patternTransform=\"translate(0, 2)\" class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488\"><rect x=\"0.5\" y=\"0.5\" width=\"5\" height=\"3\" rx=\"1\" fill=\"rgba(60, 150, 255, 1)\" class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488\"></rect></pattern><mask id=\"text-mask\" class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488\"><rect width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" fill=\"black\" class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488\"></rect><text x=\"50%\" y=\"56%\" dominant-baseline=\"middle\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"220\" font-weight=\"400\" font-family=\"&#x27;VT323&#x27;, &#x27;Space Mono&#x27;, monospace\" fill=\"white\" letter-spacing=\"18\" class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488\">MISSI</text></mask></defs><text x=\"50%\" y=\"56%\" dominant-baseline=\"middle\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"220\" font-weight=\"400\" font-family=\"&#x27;VT323&#x27;, &#x27;Space Mono&#x27;, monospace\" fill=\"#ffffff\" opacity=\"0.15\" style=\"filter:blur(12px)\" letter-spacing=\"18\" class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488\">MISSI</text><text x=\"50%\" y=\"56%\" dominant-baseline=\"middle\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"220\" font-weight=\"400\" font-family=\"&#x27;VT323&#x27;, &#x27;Space Mono&#x27;, monospace\" fill=\"#e0f2fe\" opacity=\"0.3\" style=\"filter:blur(4px)\" letter-spacing=\"18\" class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488\">MISSI</text><rect x=\"-1.5\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" fill=\"url(#led-pattern-red)\" mask=\"url(#text-mask)\" opacity=\"0.8\" class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488\"></rect><rect x=\"1.5\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" fill=\"url(#led-pattern-blue)\" mask=\"url(#text-mask)\" opacity=\"0.8\" class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488\"></rect><rect x=\"0\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" fill=\"url(#led-pattern)\" mask=\"url(#text-mask)\" class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488\"></rect></svg></div></div><h1 style=\"animation:fadeUp 0.8s ease-out 0.2s both;font-family:var(--font-ithaca)\" class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488 text-xl sm:text-2xl md:text-3xl lg:text-4xl tracking-wide leading-[1.2] max-w-3xl mb-4\">The only AI<!-- --> <span class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488 relative\">that knows you.<span style=\"background:linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.5), rgba(255,255,255,0.05))\" class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488 absolute -bottom-1 left-0 w-full h-[2px] rounded-full\"></span></span></h1><p style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4);animation:fadeUp 0.8s ease-out 0.3s both\" class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488 text-xs md:text-sm font-light leading-relaxed max-w-lg mb-8\">missiAI is a voice assistant that actually knows you. It listens, remembers, adapts — and talks back like someone who genuinely gives a damn.</p><div style=\"animation:fadeUp 0.8s ease-out 0.4s both\" class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center gap-3\"><div class=\"interactive inline-block \"><a class=\"group inline-flex items-center gap-2.5 px-7 py-3 rounded-full text-sm font-medium transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-[1.03]\" style=\"background:rgba(255,255,255,0.9);color:#000\" href=\"/chat\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-mic w-4 h-4\"><path d=\"M12 2a3 3 0 0 0-3 3v7a3 3 0 0 0 6 0V5a3 3 0 0 0-3-3Z\"></path><path d=\"M19 10v2a7 7 0 0 1-14 0v-2\"></path><line x1=\"12\" x2=\"12\" y1=\"19\" y2=\"22\"></line></svg>Try missi<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right w-4 h-4 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a></div></div><div style=\"animation:fadeUp 1.2s ease-out 0.6s both\" class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488 mt-12 w-64 h-64 flex items-center justify-center opacity-90\"><div class=\"w-full h-full flex items-center justify-center \"></div></div></div></section><section class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488 relative py-24 md:py-36 px-6 md:px-10\"><div class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488 max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center\"><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(32px);filter:blur(12px);transition:opacity 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) 0s, transform 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) 0s, filter 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) 0s\"><p style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.3)\" class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488 text-[11px] font-medium tracking-[0.25em] uppercase mb-5\">What is missiAI?</p></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(32px);filter:blur(12px);transition:opacity 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) 0.1s, transform 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) 0.1s, filter 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) 0.1s\"><h2 class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488 text-2xl md:text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight mb-6 leading-snug\">Other AIs answer questions.<!-- --> <span style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.35)\" class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488\">missi knows you.</span></h2></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(32px);filter:blur(12px);transition:opacity 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) 0.2s, transform 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) 0.2s, filter 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) 0.2s\"><p style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.45)\" class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488 text-sm md:text-base font-light leading-[1.9] max-w-2xl mx-auto\">Every voice assistant treats you like a stranger. Ask one something at 2 AM and you&#x27;ll get a Wikipedia summary. Ask missi and she&#x27;ll know you&#x27;ve been stressed about work all week, that you skipped the gym today, that you need a reminder for your sister&#x27;s birthday tomorrow — and that what you actually need isn&#x27;t information. It&#x27;s someone who remembers the full picture.</p></div></div></section><section class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488 relative py-24 md:py-32 px-6 md:px-10\"><div class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488 max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center mb-16\"><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(32px);filter:blur(12px);transition:opacity 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) 0s, transform 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) 0s, filter 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) 0s\"><p style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.3)\" class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488 text-[11px] font-medium tracking-[0.25em] uppercase mb-5\">How it works</p></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(32px);filter:blur(12px);transition:opacity 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) 0.1s, transform 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) 0.1s, filter 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) 0.1s\"><h2 class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488 text-2xl md:text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight\">Simple to start.<!-- --> <span style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.35)\" class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488\">Gets smarter over time.</span></h2></div></div><div class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488 max-w-4xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6\"><div class=\"h-full\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(32px);filter:blur(12px);transition:opacity 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) 0s, transform 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) 0s, filter 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) 0s\"><div style=\"background:rgba(255,255,255,0.04);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.09)\" class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488 relative h-full flex flex-col p-7 rounded-2xl\"><span style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.2)\" class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488 text-[10px] font-medium tracking-[0.3em] uppercase mb-5 block\">01</span><h3 class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488 text-[15px] font-medium text-white mb-2.5 tracking-tight\">Just talk</h3><p style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4)\" class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488 text-sm font-light leading-relaxed\">Open missiAI and start speaking. No setup, no forms, no training required. Your first conversation starts right now.</p></div></div><div class=\"h-full\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(32px);filter:blur(12px);transition:opacity 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) 0.1s, transform 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) 0.1s, filter 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) 0.1s\"><div style=\"background:rgba(255,255,255,0.04);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.09)\" class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488 relative h-full flex flex-col p-7 rounded-2xl\"><span style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.2)\" class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488 text-[10px] font-medium tracking-[0.3em] uppercase mb-5 block\">02</span><h3 class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488 text-[15px] font-medium text-white mb-2.5 tracking-tight\">She remembers</h3><p style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4)\" class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488 text-sm font-light leading-relaxed\">Every conversation builds your memory graph. Goals, habits, emotions, preferences — missi holds it all without you ever having to repeat yourself.</p></div></div><div class=\"h-full\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(32px);filter:blur(12px);transition:opacity 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) 0.2s, transform 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) 0.2s, filter 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) 0.2s\"><div style=\"background:rgba(255,255,255,0.04);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.09)\" class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488 relative h-full flex flex-col p-7 rounded-2xl\"><span style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.2)\" class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488 text-[10px] font-medium tracking-[0.3em] uppercase mb-5 block\">03</span><h3 class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488 text-[15px] font-medium text-white mb-2.5 tracking-tight\">She shows up first</h3><p style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4)\" class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488 text-sm font-light leading-relaxed\">Before you even ask, missi nudges you about your streak, flags what&#x27;s coming, and checks in when it matters. Proactive, personal, persistent.</p></div></div></div></section><section class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488 relative py-24 md:py-32 px-6 md:px-10\"><div class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488 max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center mb-16\"><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(32px);filter:blur(12px);transition:opacity 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) 0s, transform 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) 0s, filter 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) 0s\"><p style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.3)\" class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488 text-[11px] font-medium tracking-[0.25em] uppercase mb-5\">What missi can do</p></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(32px);filter:blur(12px);transition:opacity 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) 0.1s, transform 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) 0.1s, filter 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) 0.1s\"><h2 class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488 text-2xl md:text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight\">Built different.<!-- --> <span style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.35)\" class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488\">On purpose.</span></h2></div></div><div class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488 max-w-5xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-4\"><div class=\"h-full\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(32px);filter:blur(12px);transition:opacity 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) 0s, transform 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) 0s, filter 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) 0s\"><div style=\"background:rgba(255,255,255,0.04);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1)\" class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488 group relative h-full flex flex-col p-6 md:p-7 rounded-2xl transition-all duration-500 hover:scale-[1.02]\"><div style=\"background:radial-gradient(circle at 50% 0%, rgba(255,255,255,0.05), transparent 70%)\" class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488 absolute inset-0 rounded-2xl opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500\"></div><div class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488 relative z-10\"><div style=\"background:rgba(255,255,255,0.04);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.07)\" class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488 w-10 h-10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-waves w-4.5 h-4.5\" style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.55)\"><path d=\"M2 6c.6.5 1.2 1 2.5 1C7 7 7 5 9.5 5c2.6 0 2.4 2 5 2 2.5 0 2.5-2 5-2 1.3 0 1.9.5 2.5 1\"></path><path d=\"M2 12c.6.5 1.2 1 2.5 1 2.5 0 2.5-2 5-2 2.6 0 2.4 2 5 2 2.5 0 2.5-2 5-2 1.3 0 1.9.5 2.5 1\"></path><path d=\"M2 18c.6.5 1.2 1 2.5 1 2.5 0 2.5-2 5-2 2.6 0 2.4 2 5 2 2.5 0 2.5-2 5-2 1.3 0 1.9.5 2.5 1\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488 text-[15px] font-medium text-white mb-2 tracking-tight\">Emotional Awareness</h3><p style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4)\" class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488 text-sm font-light leading-relaxed\">Reads your tone, not just your words. Detects stress, excitement, and hesitation — and responds to what you actually feel.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"h-full\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(32px);filter:blur(12px);transition:opacity 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) 0.05s, transform 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) 0.05s, filter 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) 0.05s\"><div style=\"background:rgba(255,255,255,0.04);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1)\" class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488 group relative h-full flex flex-col p-6 md:p-7 rounded-2xl transition-all duration-500 hover:scale-[1.02]\"><div style=\"background:radial-gradient(circle at 50% 0%, rgba(255,255,255,0.05), transparent 70%)\" class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488 absolute inset-0 rounded-2xl opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500\"></div><div class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488 relative z-10\"><div style=\"background:rgba(255,255,255,0.04);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.07)\" class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488 w-10 h-10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-sparkles w-4.5 h-4.5\" style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.55)\"><path d=\"M9.937 15.5A2 2 0 0 0 8.5 14.063l-6.135-1.582a.5.5 0 0 1 0-.962L8.5 9.936A2 2 0 0 0 9.937 8.5l1.582-6.135a.5.5 0 0 1 .963 0L14.063 8.5A2 2 0 0 0 15.5 9.937l6.135 1.581a.5.5 0 0 1 0 .964L15.5 14.063a2 2 0 0 0-1.437 1.437l-1.582 6.135a.5.5 0 0 1-.963 0z\"></path><path d=\"M20 3v4\"></path><path d=\"M22 5h-4\"></path><path d=\"M4 17v2\"></path><path d=\"M5 18H3\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488 text-[15px] font-medium text-white mb-2 tracking-tight\">Persistent Memory</h3><p style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4)\" class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488 text-sm font-light leading-relaxed\">Remembers you across every session. Goals, habits, relationships — your personal graph grows with every conversation.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"h-full\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(32px);filter:blur(12px);transition:opacity 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) 0.1s, transform 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) 0.1s, filter 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) 0.1s\"><div style=\"background:rgba(255,255,255,0.04);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1)\" class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488 group relative h-full flex flex-col p-6 md:p-7 rounded-2xl transition-all duration-500 hover:scale-[1.02]\"><div style=\"background:radial-gradient(circle at 50% 0%, rgba(255,255,255,0.05), transparent 70%)\" class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488 absolute inset-0 rounded-2xl opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500\"></div><div class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488 relative z-10\"><div style=\"background:rgba(255,255,255,0.04);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.07)\" class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488 w-10 h-10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-zap w-4.5 h-4.5\" style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.55)\"><path d=\"M4 14a1 1 0 0 1-.78-1.63l9.9-10.2a.5.5 0 0 1 .86.46l-1.92 6.02A1 1 0 0 0 13 10h7a1 1 0 0 1 .78 1.63l-9.9 10.2a.5.5 0 0 1-.86-.46l1.92-6.02A1 1 0 0 0 11 14z\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488 text-[15px] font-medium text-white mb-2 tracking-tight\">Instant Voice</h3><p style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4)\" class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488 text-sm font-light leading-relaxed\">Sub-200ms latency. No awkward pauses. Conversations flow the way real ones do — fast and natural.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"h-full\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(32px);filter:blur(12px);transition:opacity 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) 0.15000000000000002s, transform 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) 0.15000000000000002s, filter 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) 0.15000000000000002s\"><div style=\"background:rgba(255,255,255,0.04);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1)\" class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488 group relative h-full flex flex-col p-6 md:p-7 rounded-2xl transition-all duration-500 hover:scale-[1.02]\"><div style=\"background:radial-gradient(circle at 50% 0%, rgba(255,255,255,0.05), transparent 70%)\" class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488 absolute inset-0 rounded-2xl opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500\"></div><div class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488 relative z-10\"><div style=\"background:rgba(255,255,255,0.04);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.07)\" class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488 w-10 h-10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-clock w-4.5 h-4.5\" style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.55)\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><polyline points=\"12 6 12 12 16 14\"></polyline></svg></div><h3 class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488 text-[15px] font-medium text-white mb-2 tracking-tight\">Proactive Intelligence</h3><p style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4)\" class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488 text-sm font-light leading-relaxed\">Missi checks in before you have to ask. Streak reminders, prep nudges, wind-down summaries — all timed to your life.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"h-full\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(32px);filter:blur(12px);transition:opacity 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) 0.2s, transform 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) 0.2s, filter 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) 0.2s\"><div style=\"background:rgba(255,255,255,0.04);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1)\" class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488 group relative h-full flex flex-col p-6 md:p-7 rounded-2xl transition-all duration-500 hover:scale-[1.02]\"><div style=\"background:radial-gradient(circle at 50% 0%, rgba(255,255,255,0.05), transparent 70%)\" class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488 absolute inset-0 rounded-2xl opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500\"></div><div class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488 relative z-10\"><div style=\"background:rgba(255,255,255,0.04);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.07)\" class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488 w-10 h-10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-lock w-4.5 h-4.5\" style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.55)\"><rect width=\"18\" height=\"11\" x=\"3\" y=\"11\" rx=\"2\" ry=\"2\"></rect><path d=\"M7 11V7a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v4\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488 text-[15px] font-medium text-white mb-2 tracking-tight\">Private by Design</h3><p style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4)\" class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488 text-sm font-light leading-relaxed\">Everything is end-to-end encrypted. Your data is never sold, never shared. Privacy is the foundation, not an afterthought.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"h-full\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(32px);filter:blur(12px);transition:opacity 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) 0.25s, transform 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) 0.25s, filter 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) 0.25s\"><div style=\"background:rgba(255,255,255,0.04);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1)\" class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488 group relative h-full flex flex-col p-6 md:p-7 rounded-2xl transition-all duration-500 hover:scale-[1.02]\"><div style=\"background:radial-gradient(circle at 50% 0%, rgba(255,255,255,0.05), transparent 70%)\" class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488 absolute inset-0 rounded-2xl opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500\"></div><div class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488 relative z-10\"><div style=\"background:rgba(255,255,255,0.04);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.07)\" class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488 w-10 h-10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-globe w-4.5 h-4.5\" style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.55)\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"M12 2a14.5 14.5 0 0 0 0 20 14.5 14.5 0 0 0 0-20\"></path><path d=\"M2 12h20\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488 text-[15px] font-medium text-white mb-2 tracking-tight\">Works Everywhere</h3><p style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4)\" class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488 text-sm font-light leading-relaxed\">Same memory, same personality, same missi — across phone, desktop, and web. Wherever you are, she is too.</p></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488 relative py-24 md:py-32 px-6 md:px-10\"><div class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488 max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center mb-16\"><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(32px);filter:blur(12px);transition:opacity 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) 0s, transform 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) 0s, filter 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) 0s\"><p style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.3)\" class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488 text-[11px] font-medium tracking-[0.25em] uppercase mb-5\">The difference</p></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(32px);filter:blur(12px);transition:opacity 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) 0.1s, transform 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) 0.1s, filter 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) 0.1s\"><h2 class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488 text-2xl md:text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight\">Every AI vs<!-- --> <span style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.35)\" class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488\">missi</span></h2></div></div><div class=\"max-w-2xl mx-auto\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(32px);filter:blur(12px);transition:opacity 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) 0s, transform 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) 0s, filter 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) 0s\"><div style=\"border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12)\" class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden\"><div style=\"background:rgba(255,255,255,0.07);border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08)\" class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488 grid grid-cols-3 gap-0 text-center text-xs font-medium py-4 px-4\"><div style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.3)\" class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488\">Feature</div><div style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.3)\" class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488\">Others</div><div class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488 text-white\">missi</div></div><div style=\"border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.07);background:rgba(255,255,255,0.03)\" class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488 grid grid-cols-3 gap-0 text-center text-sm py-3.5 px-4\"><div style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.55)\" class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488 font-light\">Remembers you</div><div style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.2)\" class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488 font-light\">Session only</div><div class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488 font-medium text-white\">Always</div></div><div style=\"border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.07);background:transparent\" class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488 grid grid-cols-3 gap-0 text-center text-sm py-3.5 px-4\"><div style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.55)\" class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488 font-light\">Understands tone</div><div style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.2)\" class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488 font-light\">—</div><div class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488 font-medium text-white\">Real-time</div></div><div style=\"border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.07);background:rgba(255,255,255,0.03)\" class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488 grid grid-cols-3 gap-0 text-center text-sm py-3.5 px-4\"><div style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.55)\" class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488 font-light\">Proactive check-ins</div><div style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.2)\" class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488 font-light\">—</div><div class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488 font-medium text-white\">Daily</div></div><div style=\"border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.07);background:transparent\" class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488 grid grid-cols-3 gap-0 text-center text-sm py-3.5 px-4\"><div style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.55)\" class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488 font-light\">Personality</div><div style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.2)\" class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488 font-light\">Robotic</div><div class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488 font-medium text-white\">Human</div></div><div style=\"border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.07);background:rgba(255,255,255,0.03)\" class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488 grid grid-cols-3 gap-0 text-center text-sm py-3.5 px-4\"><div style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.55)\" class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488 font-light\">Voice + Text</div><div style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.2)\" class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488 font-light\">Separate</div><div class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488 font-medium text-white\">Seamless</div></div><div style=\"border-bottom:none;background:transparent\" class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488 grid grid-cols-3 gap-0 text-center text-sm py-3.5 px-4\"><div style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.55)\" class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488 font-light\">Privacy</div><div style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.2)\" class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488 font-light\">Questionable</div><div class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488 font-medium text-white\">Non-negotiable</div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488 relative py-20 md:py-28 px-6\"><div style=\"background:rgba(255,255,255,0.04);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1)\" class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488 max-w-4xl mx-auto rounded-3xl px-8 py-14 md:py-20\"><div class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488 grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8 md:gap-4\"><div class=\"text-center\"><div class=\"text-3xl md:text-5xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-white mb-2\">0<!-- -->ms</div><div class=\"text-xs md:text-sm font-light tracking-wide\" style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4)\">Voice Latency</div></div><div class=\"text-center\"><div class=\"text-3xl md:text-5xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-white mb-2\">0<!-- -->%</div><div class=\"text-xs md:text-sm font-light tracking-wide\" style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4)\">Uptime</div></div><div class=\"text-center\"><div class=\"text-3xl md:text-5xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-white mb-2\">0<!-- -->k+</div><div class=\"text-xs md:text-sm font-light tracking-wide\" style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4)\">Active Users</div></div><div class=\"text-center\"><div class=\"text-3xl md:text-5xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-white mb-2\">0<!-- -->%</div><div class=\"text-xs md:text-sm font-light tracking-wide\" style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4)\">Encrypted</div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488 relative py-24 md:py-32 px-6\"><div class=\"max-w-2xl mx-auto text-center\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(32px);filter:blur(12px);transition:opacity 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) 0s, transform 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) 0s, filter 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) 0s\"><div style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.12);font-size:48px;line-height:1\" class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488 mb-6\">“</div><p style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.55)\" class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488 text-lg md:text-xl font-light leading-[1.8] italic mb-8\">I was tired of voice assistants that forget me the moment I stop talking. I wanted to build something that actually remembers — not just what I said, but why it mattered. Something that feels less like a tool, and more like someone genuinely in your corner.</p><div class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488 flex flex-col items-center gap-1\"><span style=\"font-family:var(--font-dancing-script), cursive;transform:rotate(-2deg);display:inline-block\" class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488 text-2xl italic\">Rudra S.</span><span style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.25)\" class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488 text-xs font-light\">Rudra Satani, Creator of missiAI</span></div></div></section><section class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488 relative py-24 md:py-32 px-6 text-center\"><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(32px);filter:blur(12px);transition:opacity 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) 0s, transform 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) 0s, filter 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) 0s\"><h2 class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488 text-2xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-semibold tracking-tight mb-5 max-w-xl mx-auto leading-snug\">Say something.<!-- --> <span style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.35)\" class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488\">missi is listening.</span></h2></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(32px);filter:blur(12px);transition:opacity 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) 0.1s, transform 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) 0.1s, filter 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) 0.1s\"><p style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.35)\" class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488 text-sm md:text-base font-light max-w-md mx-auto mb-10\">The future of AI isn&#x27;t artificial. It&#x27;s personal. And it starts with one conversation.</p></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(32px);filter:blur(12px);transition:opacity 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) 0.2s, transform 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) 0.2s, filter 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) 0.2s\"><div class=\"jsx-29c6afdfcb2ea488 flex flex-col sm: